<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/25(thu.) Who Listens to Google Assistant Recordings/Researchers in Israel Create First 3D-Printed Heart(Host: Cindy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=301&amp;p=317#p317"><![CDATA[
Session I Who Listens to Google Assistant Recordings?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://learningenglish.voanews.com/a/who-listens-to-google-assistant-recordings-/5002354.html">https://learningenglish.voanews.com/a/w ... 02354.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />Q1. what do you think that Google Assistant will listen and record your sounds at home?<br /><br />Q2. What do you think about personal privacy and technology convenience? <br /><br />Q3. How much privacy you can give up?<br /><br />Q4. Do you think big data makes life more convenient or it invades our personal information.<br /><br />——————————————-——————————————-——————————————-——————————————-<br /><br />Session II Researchers in Israel Create First 3D-Printed Heart<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://learningenglish.voanews.com/a/researchers-in-israel-create-first-3d-printed-heart-with-human-cells/4881547.html">https://learningenglish.voanews.com/a/r ... 81547.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />Q1. What do you think about 3D printing? And its usage in medical areas?<br /><br />Q2. what do you think if hospital routinely use 3D printing ? <br /><br />Q3. If human won’t die, what will the world be like?<br /><br />Suggested Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. free talk <br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. first topic discussion <br />8:10 p.m. --8:40 p.m. Presentation (All participants are invited)<br />8:40 p.m.-- 9.:15 p.m. second topic discussion <br />9:15 p.m.-- 9:30 p.m. Presentation<br /><br />speaker time : 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time : 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第三區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Mon Jul 22, 2019 12:35 pm</p><hr />
